name: Chain Hole
desc: When your opponent activates a monster effect in response to the activation of a card or effect: Negate that effect, and if you do, your opponent can banish 1 card from their hand or Deck with the same name as the negated card. Otherwise you can banish 1 random card from your opponent hand.
str1: Banish a card with the same name as the negated card?
str2: Banish a random card from the opponent's hand?
